          <text><![CDATA[<p>This bill directs the Department of Energy to report to Congress on&nbsp;a potential&nbsp;pilot program for the construction and operation of&nbsp;at least one micronuclear reactor (i.e., a reactor that has the thermal-power production capacity of up to 50 megawatts) to provide energy resilience&nbsp;for critical security infrastructure. </p>]]></text>
